<HEADLINE>
MAYOR THROWS SUPPORT BEHIND LAPD
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY RICK ORLOV  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES -- Mayor Richard Riordan offered a strong defense of
the Los Angeles Police Department and Chief Bernard C. Parks as he
voiced confidence the corruption scandal eng
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
