<P>
   FASHION-EDITORS _ New York _ Fashion editors live in a sort of
perpetual Australia. When everyone else is talking fall _ football
rivalries, new classes, possible Halloween costumes _ they're
thinking spring. Ask them to discuss the present, and they look a
little confused. (When pressed, can you recall details of what
occupied your thoughts six months ago?) (Sturrock, Palm Beach
Post).
</P>
