</P>
<P>
   STADIUM-TOUR (Irving, Texas) _ Texas Stadium gleams white and
blue between state routes 183 and 114. On a recent Saturday the
parking lot wasn't overflowing, just a few cars were parked near
the Pro Shop. That's where shoppers check out the latest in Cowboy
goods and where the tours of the stadium start. By JULIE COOPER.
