<SLUG> BC-GIULIANI-ART-SCANDAL-ADVISORY-NYTSF </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATTENTION ALL EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   Later today, The New York Times Syndicate will be transmitting a
oneshot article from The New York Times Magazine about Charles
