   BEUTSCHE-SAKURA-BANK (Frankfurt, Germany) _ Deutsche Bank and
Sakura Bank Ltd., Japan's fifth-largest lender, say their
securities units will jointly market bond and stock sales to
exploit growing demand for alternative financing. By Edmund L.
Andrews.
