<P>
   CHINA-CELEBRATE _ BEIJING _ New China celebrates its first half
century. Top will be on-deadline file from opening ceremonies on
Oct. 1, including what likely will be a big time military parade at
very approximately 10 p.m. EDT on Sept. 30. Bottom will include
wrap-up of the anniversary partying, who is included and excluded,
what does China have to celebrate about. (Kunstel/Albright, Cox
News Service). 30.
