   BEATTY _ BEVERLY HILLS, Calif. _ Folo on the speech made late
Wednesday night by actor-director Warren Beatty, who said he won't
let ``monied, honeyed voices of ridicule and reaction'' stop him
from considering a presidential bid. (Foskett, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
