 &UR; Carolyne Roehm  &LR; (who used to be married to tycoon &UR; Henry &LR; 
 &UR; Kravis &LR; ), &LR;  is romantically entangled with  &UR; Ed Rollins &LR; , Republican
political consultant who managed  &UR; Michael Huffington &LR; 's campaign
(and whose wife,  &UR; Sherrie Rollins &LR; , dumped him for  &UR; David &LR; 
 &UR; Westin &LR; , the president of ABC News).
</P>
<P>
   _ The San Francisco Opera having announced that its new general
director is  &UR; Pamela Rosenberg &LR; ,  &UR; Roberto-Juan Gonzalez &LR;  was
