<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-30 22:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2820 &Cx1f; taf-z
u p BC-R-BEATTY-SCENE-ART-NY     09-30 0606
